=== Scenario 1: basic drop ===
--- before drop ---
1	x
1	y
2	z
3	w
--- after drop partition 2 ---
1	x
1	y
3	w
--- after drop partition 99 (no-op) ---
1	x
1	y
3	w
--- after dropping all partitions ---
0
NOT_IMPLEMENTED
=== Scenario 2: multi-partition drop, then drop again, counts stay sane ===
--- before any drop ---
5
--- after drop partition 'a' ---
4
2	b
3	c
4	d
5	e
--- after drop partition 'b' ---
3
=== Scenario 3: multiple files per partition ===
--- before drop ---
1	x
1	y
1	z
2	p
--- after drop partition 1 ---
2	p
=== Scenario 4: drop then re-insert ===
1	new
2	keep
=== Scenario 5: drop after DELETE FROM (position-deletes present) ===
2	keep
